<h1 id="pivot">Pivot</h1>
<p>A layout component that allows a user to switch between different sets of content or filters on the content currently visible. This is in contrast to a purely navigational UI element such as NavBar or a commanding element such as CommandBar. An example
    would be Read vs. Unread items in the Outlook Web App.</p>
